{"tid":1627724,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"裝修單野，大家幾時先肯明文宣組要做的係文宣唔係割席？","createTime":"2019-10-05T17:23:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-06T06:28:58.000Z","uid":23991,"like":11,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"eeca0e5308b87b6737efa584f5b96a7bd8348696","tid":1627724,"uid":23991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T17:23:19.000Z","msg":"裝修除左係令賣港鋪頭冇得做生意同要比錢維修<br />\n最重要的係對準共黨政權 比個好撚強的message全世界聽<br />\n我地要支共同賣港的仆街屎都冇得食<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我承應打中資同賣港鋪之途中<br />\n難免有機會誤中副車 特別係用魔法/有黑警搞事<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/photo.php?fbid=10157510292609929&amp;set=a.396735049928&amp;type=3&amp;theater\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fphoto.php%3Ffbid%3D10157510292609929%26set%3Da.396735049928%26type%3D3%26theater&d=AECyLZWdcqpY%2FGgvZN2GpFQYB6qXEwX4CB7r1YlVkGU%3D&h=9ab2222f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/photo.php?fbid=10157510292609929&amp;set=a.396735049928&amp;type=3&amp;theater</a><br />\n<br />\n呢刻就算手足唔裝修都會有黑警去搞事<br />\n無論係黑警定手足做<br />\n和理組應該要做的係搵方法補償被誤中的商戶同認錯道歉<br />\n<br />\n做好個公關<br />\n對準支共同賣港鋪裝修 目標正確 點都唔割<br />\n<br />\n我係垃圾得把口<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有冇手足一齊幫下手可以點做好個公關<br />\n同岩聽唔該幫我推下po<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"774032df985d828562280d262261c4f3c1afe4dc","tid":1627724,"uid":236281,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T17:23:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/n1ZhMhv.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fn1ZhMhv.jpg&h=128ca870&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a9e2db2a1a912c0417002a12c482856a9e551654","tid":1627724,"uid":187510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T17:25:49.000Z","msg":"無人割過 只係俾建議點樣裝修 同幫邊間鋪裝修"},{"pid":"a62810ffa6c862302e78369ab5492f19593f